Package: grfxtools
Title: An R package of tools to assist with various plotting tasks
Version: 0.1.0
Author:Thomas Muench [aut, cre], Andrew Dolman [aut]
Maintainer: Thomas Muench <thomas.muench@awi.de>
Description: This package contains various functions to
    assist with the plotting of scientific results incl. geoscientific
    maps; mostly applying tidyverse/ggplot2 functionality.
License: file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/EarthSystemDiagnostics/grfxtools
BugReports:
    https://github.com/EarthSystemDiagnostics/grfxtools/issues
Depends:
    R (>= 3.5)
Imports:
    dplyr (>= 1.0.2),
    ggforce (>= 0.3.1),
    ggplot2 (>= 3.2.1),
    maptools (>= 0.9.9),
    raster (>= 3.0.7),
    rgeos (>= 0.5.2),
    scales (>= 1.1.1),
    tibble (>= 3.0.4),
    tidyr (>= 1.1.2)
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.1.1
